OUR RESTAURANT
body: Our dishes are freshly prepared in-house with our special 'Indian Ocean recipe', which excludes all artificial colourings and preservatives. And all our dishes are served steaming hot into a special stay fresh packaging, ready to collect or be delivered to your door step.

name: Meal for 2
title: OUR FOOD
body: Eating out is more than just food. It is about atmosphere, about ambience, but above all taste!We have installed some of India's history, culture and beliefs into creating the perfect authentic feel for you. If you want to create your own dish, a little hotter, a little creamier? No problem. We allow our customers the option to customize to their suitable needs. Just ask us and we will cook it to order at no extra cost
